c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Relume and Tome share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Ai Generation, Collaboration. On the other hand, Tome uniquely offers Brand Kit and Animations and Stock Assets, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Relume holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Tome scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Relume and Tome offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Relume's free tier and Tome's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
